<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="11Sep1938"><font color="red">11 September 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): We plan to leave here tomorrow Friday at 4 p.m. (12 September 1938 was a Monday) and get off at Dijon, hotel de la cloche &hellip; I should like to spend a few days in fresh air, or fairly fresh compared to Dijon &hellip; Ask F and F for more page proofs as I want to check all Part I together. </div>
